meta.prompt: A resplendent golden warrior,clad in emerald-tinged armor etched with crimson runes,stands triumphant atop a windswept hill,his hammer raised high in devotion to Sigmar. The scene,reminiscent of Frazetta's dynamic compositions and Turner's ethereal lighting,bathes in a celestial glow that pierces through ominous storm clouds. Swirling brushstrokes evoke Van Gogh's turbulent skies,while Klimt-inspired geometric patterns adorn the warrior's flowing cape. The landscape below unfolds in a tapestry of verdant fields and amber wheat,punctuated by scarlet poppies that dance in an unseen breeze. A distant citadel,its spires reaching skyward,gleams with an otherworldly radiance,its architecture a fusion of Gothic and Art Nouveau styles. The air crackles with tangible energy,hinting at imminent divine intervention. Hyper-detailed textures bring every element to life,from the weathered leather of the warrior's gauntlets to the individual blades of grass at his feet. A sense of epic scale pervades the composition,with the warrior dominating the foreground while the vast,tumultuous world stretches endlessly behind him. The overall mood is one of awe-inspiring power tempered by a touch of melancholy,as if capturing a fleeting moment of glory before the tides of fate shift once more.,
